### Feed Service API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/feed

### Parameters - Update these with actual values
@postId = test-post-id
@commentId = test-commend-id
@userId = test-user-id

### ============================================
### POST ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Get all posts (feed)
GET {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

### ============================================
### COMMENT ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Get all comments for a post
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{postId}}/comments
Content-Type: application/json

### Create a new comment
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{postId}}/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": "user-123",
    "content": "This is a test comment"
}

### ============================================
### REACTION ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Add or update a reaction on a post (HELPFUL)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/{{postId}}/reactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": "{{userId}}",
    "reactionType": "HELPFUL"
}

### Get my reaction on a post
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{postId}}/reactions/me?userId={{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get all reactions for a post
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{postId}}/reactions
Content-Type: application/json

### Remove my reaction from a post
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{postId}}/reactions?userId={{userId}}